                  </persName>
            , Imperial fire-office, Falmouth; she is an <rs id="t18320105-4-viclabel24" type="occupation">agent to the office</rs> - I placed the letter in the letter-rack, for the messenger to take to the Post-office, about three o'clock.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320105-4-person171">
                  SAMUEL 
                  INGALL
               <interp inst="t18320105-4-person171" type="surname" value="INGALL"></interp>
